21","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited building over graves, sitting upon them, or praying over them. Source: Musnad Abi\u0304 Ya\u2019la\u0301 1020 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37223,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/25\/resurrected-deen-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":17347,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Resurrection: Each resurrected with their religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery servant in his grave will be resurrected upon the way he died, the believer upon his faith and the hypocrite upon his hypocrisy.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 14722 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/fai